    "subject": "Criminal Law & Protections - Fourth Amendment",
    "rule": "Exclusionary Rule and Exceptions (Fruits of Poisonous Tree, Good Faith, Inevitable Discovery)",
    "question": "When does evidence become a 'fruit of the poisonous tree' subject to exclusion under the Fourth Amendment?",
