    "notes": "**Express Easement Elements:**\n- **Identifiable servient land** (the burdened property)\n- **Identifiable dominant land** (the benefited property, if appurtenant)\n- **Clear statement of the right or privilege** (e.g., right of way)\n- **Intent to create a permanent/long-term interest**\n\n**Writing Requirement:**\n- Must satisfy **Statute of Frauds** (writing signed by grantor required)\n- **Exception:** Easement by estoppel/part performance may overcome SoF in some jurisdictions\n- **No parol evidence** to modify or create express easement terms",
