    "notes": "- **Extent is determined by the scope of the stated purpose**\n- Easement holder may use only **so much of the servient land as reasonably necessary** for the intended use\n- **Reasonable person standard** applies: What amount of land is functionally needed?\n- Servient tenant retains right to object to **unreasonably expansive use** of the easement area\n- **Burden on easement holder** to limit use to necessary, reasonable dimensions",
