    "notes": "- **Original purpose governs apportionment**; expansion to serve additional properties = **scope violation**\n- **Each new parcel cannot automatically inherit the easement benefit** unless explicitly granted or clearly intended\n- **Burden on new dominant owners** to prove the original grant contemplated multiple properties\n- Increased intensity of use beyond original scope = **actionable by servient tenant**\n- Exception: **Easement in gross** (personal to one party) generally **cannot be apportioned or assigned** without servient tenant consent",
