    "trigger": "A lawyer represents a client in a contract dispute but delays filing the complaint for three months without client agreement or legitimate reason.",
    "notes": "- **Core duty**: Lawyer must act with **reasonable diligence and promptness** in representing a client\n- Standard is **objective reasonableness**, not gross negligence\n- Applies to **all matters** undertaken on behalf of client\n- Failure to meet this duty = breach of fiduciary obligation\n- Rule focuses on **speed and consistency of effort**, not outcome",
